text: Princess Unikitty is a fictional character from the movie The Lego Movie and its own spinoff series Unikitty!. She was voiced by Alison Brie in the movie series and Tara Strong in the animated series. ==History== Unikitty lives in Cloud Coo-Coo Land in the first movie, and its own Unikingdom in the TV series. ==Reception== Unikitty’s character received generally positive reviews who praised Brie’s performances. ==References== Category:Animated characters Category:Fictional cats Category:Anthromophic characters Category:Fictional characters introduced in 2014
